    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a showroom-quality E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example boasts impeccable mechanical provenance, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The suspension remains taut, preserving the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and analog steering feedback. A turn-key, collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
